                <summary>The members of the conservative party in the congressional district
                    including Augusta will meet in Harrisburg on October 5th to select a candidate
                    for congress. Each county and city will be entitled to a delegate and a vote for
                    every 100 registered voters. John B. Baldwin and James H. Williams issued the
                    notice.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
